  <steps>
    <step order="1">Load r1 ledger entry RB-T028-08 (lines ~856-897) for documented symptom + two hypotheses.</step>
    <step order="2">Verify task 011 (Phase 1 cluster fix) is complete and merged. Read its commit message for the registration-path change.</step>
    <step order="3">First check: temporarily remove the `Skip = "..."` attribute on `PostPrecedent_AsAdmin_Returns_201_WithTentativeStatus` and run the integration test: `dotnet test tests/integration/Spe.Integration.Tests/ --filter "FullyQualifiedName~PrecedentAdminEndpointsTests.PostPrecedent_AsAdmin_Returns_201_WithTentativeStatus"`. If it passes after task 011, this is Hypothesis 1: close as `repaired` with cross-reference (skip to step 8).</step>
    <step order="4">If still failing, read `src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Api/Insights/PrecedentAdminEndpoints.cs` `PostPrecedent` handler and the `IPrecedentService` interface (likely under `Services/Insights/`). Compare the method name being called against the test's Moq expectation (`CreateTentativeAsync`).</step>
    <step order="5">If signature drift (Hypothesis 2): update the Moq expectation in the test to match the actual service method name. Test-only edit; commit cites RB-T028-08 + `repaired` resolution mode.</step>
    <step order="6">If genuine production gap (Hypothesis 3): determine the correct method to call OR contact the `ai-spaarke-insights-engine-r1` owner. If production fix required, implement the minimal change to `PostPrecedent` to invoke the expected service method. If sibling-owned, mark `transferred-to-sibling` and file in their backlog.</step>
    <step order="7">Build + test as appropriate: `dotnet build` for any production change; `dotnet test --filter ...PrecedentAdminEndpointsTests` for verification. Re-enabled test must pass.</step>
    <step order="8">Update ledger row RB-T028-08: status → `repaired` (or `transferred-to-sibling` if applicable), add fix-commit SHA + today's date + cross-reference to task 011 if Hypothesis 1.</step>
    <step order="9">Commit: `fix(bff-api): close PrecedentAdmin endpoint verification gap (RB-T028-08; repaired)` (adjust message to fit resolution mode) per NFR-04.</step>
    <step order="10">Update `projects/sdap.bff.api-test-suite-repair-r2/current-task.md` with completion + chosen hypothesis + commit SHA.</step>
  </steps>

